WEBVTT

00:01.710 --> 00:07.006
It possesses enormous power,
and brings endless pleasure--

00:07.090 --> 00:10.968
and destruction-- to those who are destined.

23:16.228 --> 23:18.020
After all, you‘re my mom!

23:18.105 --> 23:20.648
I hate the Child Welfare lady!

23:20.732 --> 23:24.652
Why does she always try to separate us?!

23:24.736 --> 23:26.237
Let's run away again.

23:26.321 --> 23:28.572
To someplace nobody will follow us.

23:28.657 --> 23:31.659
And then we can build a
house and live in it together!

23:31.743 --> 23:33.661
i made blueprints!

23:33.745 --> 23:35.830
I‘ll show them to you next time, Mom!

23:35.914 --> 23:37.998
We‘ll always be together from now on.

23:38.083 --> 23:39.917
Right, Mom?
